fields.name: MediManage
fields.description: Creating a comprehensive healthcare management system for clinics and hospitals. The system will manage patient records, appointments, billing, and medical history, aiming to streamline healthcare operations and improve patient care.

fields.name: Skyline Realty
fields.description: Skyline Realty is an ambitious project to build a modern, responsive, and scalable web application for managing real estate listings. The app will feature advanced search capabilities, interactive maps, and a seamless user interface to enhance the user experience for both buyers and sellers.
